title: 8 AM Hour - The WORST Lyric Shuffle Round?
description:
Hey everyone! We had mixed reactions with posting the show in hours like this, let us know if you like the show separated by hour, or if you like it posted as one show as one (like we did before) Thanks!

Lyric Shuffle: Falen vs Drake, Jenny has a story about a hookup, Who give's the best advice?, & More!
